{
  "stem": "1479.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Assigned to work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As you know that Schindler took over a Jewish factory that was producing pots and pans before the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How he took over the factory, later on we found out, he was advised by some Jewish people when he came to Poland looking, seeking fortunes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was advised to take over this factory because this was a good item for the black market.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he can make a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were working over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were assigned to work at painting and producing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is not the one process, you just paint.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There's a whole series of processes before you make the finished product.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was assigned first-- first as a helper to the painter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "However, the manager noticed that i was very good with my hands.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was assigned to be a painter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the painter also-- there was white paint.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there was the red paint.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The red paint was more complicated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But when I was assigned to do something, I tried my best.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I succeeded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I managed to do it because, by doing so, I noticed and I learned quickly, I could avoid many unpleasant things from the managers and other things.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So they were pleased with my work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I had a-- a little bit more peace and quiet doing my job.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time was a Polish manager.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then there was also a Jewish man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they were always on top.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had all kinds of managers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But of course, there was Nazis, professionals.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, you needed all kinds.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How to start, to make from nothing, to create a shape and-- and to make it-- and then-- the process was a long process.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was very curious.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
